text: Ursula Brauch (born 18 October 1962) is a German rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Karlsruhe
